Harry looks at Albus - moved. #CursedChild
Ginny: Harry, you'd do anything for everybody. You were pretty happy to sacrifice yourself for the world. #CursedChild

Draco: We can hug too if you like ... #CursedChild

Delphi: That's the thing isn't it? About friendships. You don't know what he needs. You only know he needs it. #CursedChild

Ginny: If you don't behave, Ronald Weasley,  I will tell Mum 
Ron: Nothing scares me. Apart from Mum. #CursedChild

Albus: Hello, Dad. Is something wrong? 
Harry looks at his son disbelievingly. #CursedChild
